{"books":[{"id":"78256f65-d15b-4800-976e-d4a9e6e7a160","name":"红旗一九五八年第二期","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"《红旗》杂志编辑部","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives2/main/78256f65-d15b-4800-976e-d4a9e6e7a160.pdf"],"article":{"title":"为啥云上红旗飘","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"title","text":"为啥云上红旗飘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朵朵白云天空飘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朵朵云上红旗摇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是不是天兵开了战，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为啥云上红旗飘？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":" "},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仔细看，仔细瞧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘿！社员垦荒在山腰。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头顶蓝天手拿镐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驾着云雾满山跑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":" "},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“要和神仙比高低！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喊声冲上九重霄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"硬石头上种五谷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白云上面栽仙桃。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":" "},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳出海大吃惊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吓得虎狼到处逃。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明天要去闹天宫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夺取天河浇仙桃。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":" "}],"authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1958}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"（山东单县民歌）","page_start":39,"page_end":39},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}